de.latlon.deejump.wfs.client

Class AbstractWFSWrapper

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.latlon.deejump.wfs.client.AbstractWFSWrapper
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    WFServiceWrapper_1_0_0, WFServiceWrapper_1_1_0

    public abstract class AbstractWFSWrapper
extends Object
    Superclass that wraps the basic functionality of a (simple) WFS. This class encapsulates the behaviour of a WFS, and allows subclasses to change behaviour according to WFS version.
    Version:
    $Revision: 1438 $, $Date: 2008-05-29 15:00:02 +0200 (Do, 29 Mai 2008) $
    Author:
    Ugo Taddei, last edited by: $Author: stranger $
